Title: ACS Surgery: Principles and Practice
Author: ডগলাস ডব্লিউ. উইলমোর
Summary: Harvard Medical School, Boston, MA. Previously titled Scientific American Surgery. Aims to apply the best of current surgical thinking to the practice of modern surgery. A supplemental CD-ROM is forthcoming. Illustrated in a variety of formats. DNLM: Surgical Procedures, Operative--methods.
